title: Best Hot Dogs in NYC to Try Now
seo_title: Best Hot Dogs in NYC to Try Now | WestHouse
seo_description: New York is world famous for its hot dogs. They're in almost every film, and they're on almost every block. While you can always stop at a Sabrett street cart (there are hundreds throughout Manhattan), we prefer these gourmet hot dog spots.
